{"File":"/home/ketan/eagerminds-task/.gemini/transcript","LineNumber":313,"LineContent":"      \"content\": \"The authentication system is fully implemented. Here's a concise overview:\\n\\n## What was built\\n\\n**14 files total** \\u2014 all TypeScript compiles with zero errors.\\n\\n### Supabase Client Layer (`src/lib/supabase/`)\\n- [client.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/lib/supabase/client.ts) \\u2014 Browser client via `createBrowserClient` (auto-uses `document.cookie`)\\n- [server.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/lib/supabase/server.ts) \\u2014 Server client via `createServerClient` + `cookies()` from `next/headers`\\n- [middleware.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/lib/supabase/middleware.ts) \\u2014 Session refresh helper + `/dashboard` auth guard\\n\\n### Proxy (Next.js 16 replaces `middleware.ts` with `proxy.ts`)\\n- [proxy.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/proxy.ts) \\u2014 Uses the **new `proxy` export** (the `middleware` convention is deprecated in v16). Refreshes tokens on every request and redirects unauthenticated `/dashboard` visitors to `/login`.\\n\\n### Auth Pages\\n- [login/page.tsx](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/login/page.tsx) \\u2014 Split-screen layout, dark glassmorphic design, violet gradient CTA\\n- [signup/page.tsx](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/signup/page.tsx) \\u2014 Same design language with fuchsia-violet accents, name/email/password fields\\n\\n### Server Actions \u0026 API Routes\\n- [actions/auth.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/actions/auth.ts) \\u2014 `login()` and `signup()` server actions; signup triggers the welcome email\\n- [api/welcome-email/route.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/api/welcome-email/route.ts) \\u2014 POSTs to Resend API with a rich dark-themed HTML email\\n- [auth/callback/route.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/auth/callback/route.ts) \\u2014 PKCE code exchange for email confirmation\\n\\n### Protected Route\\n- [dashboard/page.tsx](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/dashboard/page.tsx) \\u2014 Minimal placeholder with sign-out; double-checks auth server-side\\n\\nNo database tables or bookmarks schema were created, as instructed.\""}
