{"File":"/home/ketan/eagerminds-task/.gemini/transcript","LineNumber":4081,"LineContent":"      \"content\": \"Yes, **Resend is fully integrated and ready to be used!** \\n\\nHere is how the setup works and what you need to know:\\n\\n### 1. The Configuration\\nYour API key is already configured in [.env.local](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/.env.local#L3):\\n```env\\nRESEND_API_KEY=re_KYAgBJnJ_4CGk4zzga45RiQPAoLXtPSfP\\n```\\nThe integration doesn't require any npm package because it uses the native `fetch` API inside [route.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/api/welcome-email/route.ts#L31) to send the request directly to `https://api.resend.com/emails`.\\n\\n### 2. How it's Triggered\\nWhen a user signs up on the `/signup` page, the server action [auth.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/actions/auth.ts#L63-L72) fires a non-blocking `fetch` request to the `/api/welcome-email` API endpoint:\\n```typescript\\nfetch(`${baseUrl}/api/welcome-email`, {\\n  method: \\\"POST\\\",\\n  headers: { \\\"Content-Type\\\": \\\"application/json\\\" },\\n  body: JSON.stringify({ email, name }),\\n});\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n### \\u26a0\\ufe0f Important Testing Notes\\n\\nIf you are using a **free/unverified Resend account**:\\n1. **Testing Restrictions**: Resend restricts unverified accounts to sending emails **only to the email address you used to register your Resend account**. If you sign up using a different email address on your signup page, Resend will reject the email request.\\n2. **From Address**: The current sender in [route.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/api/welcome-email/route.ts#L38) is set to:\\n   ```typescript\\n   from: \\\"Bookmarks \u003conboarding@resend.dev\u003e\\\"\\n   ```\\n   This domain (`resend.dev`) only works for sending emails to your own registered test address.\\n\\n### To Go Live (Production Setup):\\nOnce you want to send emails to all users:\\n1. Add and verify your custom domain in the **Resend Dashboard**.\\n2. Update the `from` field in [route.ts](file:///home/ketan/eagerminds-task/src/app/api/welcome-email/route.ts#L38) to use your verified domain (e.g., `from: \\\"Bookmarks \u003cwelcome@yourdomain.com\u003e\\\"`).\""}
